	   <tr><td colspan=2>What you need to collect in order to make the Reinforced Cobalt Hide Leggings:<br><br>Bricks of Velium that drop in Crystal Caverns (the unstackable ones--minimum needed is 3 but i'd get 5 or 6)<br><br>Drake Eggs (1 needed; can forage them in Skyshrine but it takes forever even with 155 foraging skill...good luck!)<br><br>Cobalt Drake Hides (1 needed)<br><br>Coldain Velium Temper (buy this near mines in Thurgadin for around 25pp a piece)<br><br>File (see below)<br><br>You need smithing to combine the File, Coldain Velium Temper and Velium Brick in order to get a VELIUM BONING.  You need THREE BONINGS FOR THE LEGGINGS. Then you need a brewer to combine the DRAKE EGG and a FLASK of water to make Drake Egg Oil.  Then take the BONINGS and tailor it with a PATTERN, the DRAKE EGG OIL, and the DRAKE HIDE.<br><br>Oh, and hope your tailor doesn't fail.  OR the brewer you're using.  Or even the smith.  <br><br>:)<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>Wayzup Wanderon<br>Wandering Wood Elf Ranger<br>Hmm, that's strange...Oh wait, that's ME that's strange.</td></tr>
