	   <tr><td colspan=2>Aye, for those thinking that you can just get tailoring up and make these with no trial ... you are in for a nasty surprise. The failure rates on most Velious tailoring over crystalline are just painful (because trivial skyrockets). If you really want a pair of these I would suggest you find a tailor with high skill and give them the components and hope they do not fail (as stated above). This would be MUCH easier and less time consuming. Not to mention it would give the tailor a chance to skill up. Always a good thing!<br><br>Tramaus Voronadil<br>30th Paladin of Truth - Acropolis<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
